snippet: Top-seeded Novak Djokovic was upset by No. 13 Jo-Wilfried Tsonga, 6-2, 6-2, in the third round of the Rogers Cup in Toronto.
abstract: Jo-Wilfred Tsonga upsets Novak Djokovic in third round of Rogers Cup in Toronto; other tennis news noted.

headline.main: Tsonga Ousts Djokovic From Rogers Cup
